ing: 1 (8 ounce) package cream cheese, cut into pieces
des: "Great vegetarian crock pot recipe from my mom. Ground turkey or grilled chicken added to the finished product are great additions for meat lovers. Italian-style diced tomatoes can also be added."
ins:
Stir vegetable broth, tortellini, cream cheese, spinach, and mushrooms together in a slow cooker.
Cook on Low for 5 to 6 hours.
